<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

158
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wake up, Kinoshita-san!</font>

159
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! No!</font>

160
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kinoshita-san! Wake up!</font>

161
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Man, that startled me.</i></font>

162
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please wake up!</font>

163
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gloomyhara-san's acting differently 
than he usually does.</i></font>

164
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so sorry! It's all my fault!</font>

165
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What should I do?</font>

166
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess being removed from
 the center position really got to him.</i></font>

