356
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

357
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm currently working, so...</font>

358
00:18:14,930 --> 00:18:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll humbly accept the thought, though.</font>

359
00:18:19,370 --> 00:18:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, no. I made Tamon-kun sad.</i></font>

360
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I just can't...</i></font>

361
