<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

363
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat it.</font>

364
00:18:40,420 --> 00:18:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even just a bite.</font>

365
