<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. Please?</font>

366
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open up.</font>

367
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Accept it... All of my love.</font>

368
00:18:57,840 --> 00:18:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tamon-kun, no...</i></font>

369
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We mustn't...</i></font>

370
00:19:06,410 --> 00:19:07,960
