on a completely random day.</i></font>

377
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

378
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Gloomy, gloom... Gloomy, gloom...</i></font>

379
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had been treating Tamon-kun like 
a cute little needy puppy...</i></font>

380
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then he got all weird to the point</i></font>

381
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I'm getting worried that 
he might not even be from this planet.</i></font>

382
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have some cola, too.</font>

383
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you very much.</font>

384
00:19:56,140 --> 00:20:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He... totally flipped his switch 
