This is dangerous.</i></font>

394
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should get going.</font>

395
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Already?</font>

396
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This fanservice is so extreme...</i></font>

397
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's basically devaluing 
himself as an idol.</i></font>

398
00:20:43,730 --> 00:20:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't let this escalate any further.</i></font>

399
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take the rest home with me. 
Could I borrow an ice pack?</font>

