00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... sure.</font>

401
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to keep my distance.</i></font>

402
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:59,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being overprotective isn't always love.</i></font>

403
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need him to be able to 
survive on his own.</i></font>

404
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san, you've got some 
