00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're closer than that, aren't we, Utage?</font>

412
00:21:34,690 --> 00:21:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He...</i></font>

413
